    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know, i know, i should probably go. but honestly i'm just super busy with work this week and an appointment will take forever. the pain isn't even that bad, it's more just annoying. i really think it's just the screen time causing it. if i just use the drops like 4 or 5 times a day, won't that help soothe the irritation enough that i can just wait until the weekend to see a doctor? it doesn't seem like an emergency.",
