    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get what you're saying but i've used these exact same drops for eye strain before and they always work. it's just so much more convenient to try this first. and if the crusty stuff doesn't go away, i can just get some of those redness-relief drops too? like visine or something? that should definitely get the redness out of there pretty quickly. wouldn't that be a better way to manage it for now?",
